'''Talalit''' neɣ '''Amasilul''' d [[tagaska]] tis snat ilan azal yakk deg [[Tamasiḥit|tmasiḥt]] seld n [[Tanekra (tagaska)|tnekra]] id yesskanayen asmekti n [[talallit n Yissu|tlallit n Yisus]], Tafaska ayyi tebeddu deg yiṭ n [[24 dujamber|24 dujember]] d wass n [[25 dujamber|25 dujember]] deg [[Taswast tagrigurt|teswast tagrigurt]] d [[taswast tayulyant|teswast tayulyant]] maca s usrag n umgarad n snat n teswasin-a s 13 n wussan tettili-d tfaska n tlalit deg [[tamezdayt (Asɣan)|tmezdayin]] yeṭṭafaren taswast tayulyant deg yiṭ n [[6 yennayer]] d wass n [[7 yennayer]] ɣas akken [[Tibibelt|ibibel]] ur d-ibdir ara ass neɣ azmez n tlallit n [[Ɛisa|Yissu]] maca [[ibabaten n tmezdayt]] ssidgen-d azmez-a d akken-t d asihar-is (ttiɛad-is) seg useggas n [[325]]. Akken daɣen yettusismel unasay n tmezdayt s umeggez-ines deg tlemmast n yiṭ. Yerna yettwabdar-d deg ''injil n tegrudt n Yakuf'' deg [[Tasut tis 3|tsut tis kṛad]] anelfuy-a (aneḍruy-a) yella-d deg tlemmast n yiṭ, d akken ababat [[Pius PP. XI]] deg [[tamezdayt takatukikt|tmezdayt takatulikt]] yessentem (iwekked) deg [[1921]] d akken anelfuy-a yella-d deg tlemmast n yiṭ s talɣa tamaddudt akken id yebder daɣen d akken send n tmasiḥt ass n 25 dujember yella-d tafaska [[tinnedmemt]] i wsemɣer n [[tafukt|tfukt]]
